{
  "texts": [
    "The main purpose of this paper is to introduce natural language processing (NLP) in an actuarial context.",
    "We start with a brief overview of NLP and traditional approaches, and then provide an introduction to NLP using transformers.",
    "We provide an overview of different workflows to incorporate NLP into actuarial contexts.",
    "We apply the concepts to two datasets that are typical in actuarial applications.",
    "The first dataset contains verbal descriptions of car accidents in both English and German language, as well as some tabular data such as the number of vehicles involved and the presence of bodily injury."
  ]
}